<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">

<head>
  <title>Brave UX - Work - Upside</title>
  <%- include ../partials/_head %>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include ../partials/_menu %>
    <main class="wrapper case-study upside">
      <header class="case-header">
        <div class="case-header-content container">
          <h5 class="case-header-client-name">Upside</h5>
          <h1 class="case-header-tagline">Travel that takes&nbsp;
            <br />care of business</h1>
          <h6 class="case-header-type">Business Travel Application</h6>
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class="case-exec-summary padded yellow">
        <div class="container">
          <p class="case-exec-summary-text">The founder of Priceline.com set his sights on business travel, and&nbsp;we&nbsp;created a product that turns the
            industry on its head.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="case-breakdown padded gray">
        <div class="container row">
          <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
            <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Challenge</p>
            <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
              Travel for business has never been worse
            </h3>
            <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
              Before you even get to the plane, a maze of shifting flights, hotels and meetings awaits you. And there&rsquo;s no real incentive
              for anyone to try harder.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
            <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Solution</p>
            <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
              Show users the formula, and reward them
            </h3>
            <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
              A model that you can tinker with is paired with real savings and gift cards to empower and motivate users.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
            <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Scope</p>
            <ul class="case-breakdown-list">
              <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Brand System</li>
              <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Information Architecture</li>
              <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Interaction Design</li>
              <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Front-end Development</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="block padded orange">
        <div class="row container">
          <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md gutter-bottom-mobile column half-md one-third-xl">
            <div class="inner-block-content gutter-right">
              <h2 class="case-block-heading">What&rsquo;s in it for you</h2>
              <p class="case-block-text">
                Upside rewards users who are flexible—with real gift cards to their favorite retailers—all while saving their company money.
                We created a series of intuitive infographics to explain this concept.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="inner-block column column-block align-self-center half-md two-third-xl">
            <div class="frame frame-desktop dark sr-right lazy-ratio" data-width="1150" data-height="737">
              <img class="inner-block-image" alt="Rewards landing page for Upside" data-normal="./images/work/upside/rewards.jpg" data-srcset="
                  ./images/work/upside/rewards@0.5x.jpg 575w,
                  ./images/work/upside/rewards.jpg 1150w,
                  ./images/work/upside/rewards@1.5x.jpg 1725w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 90vw, (max-width: 1440px) 45vw, 810px">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="block">
        <img class="block-image half-height" alt="Image of an airplane aisle with Upside price tags popping up around different seats on the plane."
          data-normal="./images/work/upside/airplane-banner.jpg" data-srcset="
            ./images/work/upside/airplane-banner@0.5x.jpg 700w,
            ./images/work/upside/airplane-banner.jpg 1400w,
            ./images/work/upside/airplane-banner@1.5x.jpg 2100w" sizes=" 100vw">
      </section>

      <section class="block row">
        <div class="inner-block column column-block half-md hide-overflow yellow">
          <div class="lazy-ratio full-height" data-width="136" data-height="150">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/upside/details-1.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-top">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/upside/details-2.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-left">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/upside/details-3.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-right">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column order-top-xs half-md gray">
          <div class="inner-block-content container">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Goodbye, forms</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              Getting the details of your trip shouldn&rsquo;t feel like an interrogation. We rethought and resequenced how users plan
              their trips, so they understand what&rsquo;s going on and why.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="block dark-purple">
        <img data-normal="./images/work/upside/plane-bg.svg" alt="" class="block-image half-height">
        <img data-normal="./images/work/upside/plane.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-left">
      </section>

      <section class="block padded">
        <div class="inner-block padded-bottom row absolute-center-md">
          <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Try a trip on for size</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              We got rid of sluggish search results of endless, identical-looking options. Instead, users can easily change any part of
              their trips, and quickly see the impact.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block upside-interface">
          <div class="container-narrow">
            <div class="frame frame-desktop dark shadow sr-bottom lazy-ratio" data-width="1800" data-height="1016">
              <img class="inner-block-image" alt="Screen of the app going through the process of booking a flight" data-normal="./images/work/upside/interface.jpg"
                data-srcset="
                  ./images/work/upside/interface@0.5x.jpg 900w,
                  ./images/work/upside/interface@0.75x.jpg 1350w,
                  ./images/work/upside/interface.jpg 1800w" sizes="80vw">
            </div>
            <img class="inner-block-image contain absolute sr-left sr-delay-double" alt="Background image of a random screen within the app"
              data-normal="./images/work/upside/interface-bg1.jpg" data-srcset="
                  ./images/work/upside/interface-bg1@0.5x.jpg 450w,
                  ./images/work/upside/interface-bg1@0.75x.jpg 675w,
                  ./images/work/upside/interface-bg1.jpg 900w" sizes="75vw">
            <img class="inner-block-image contain absolute sr-right sr-delay-double" alt="Background image of a random screen within the app"
              data-normal="./images/work/upside/interface-bg2.jpg" data-srcset="
                  ./images/work/upside/interface-bg2@0.5x.jpg 450w,
                  ./images/work/upside/interface-bg2@0.75x.jpg 675w,
                  ./images/work/upside/interface-bg2.jpg 900w" sizes="75vw">
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="block">
        <img class="block-image half-height" alt="Image of an airplane terminal walkway with Upside purple and yellow brand colors adorning it."
          data-normal="./images/work/upside/terminal-banner.jpg" data-srcset="
            ./images/work/upside/terminal-banner@0.5x.jpg 599w,
            ./images/work/upside/terminal-banner.jpg 1198w,
            ./images/work/upside/terminal-banner@1.5x.jpg 1797w" sizes="100vw">
      </section>

      <section class="block row">
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column half-md gray">
          <div class="inner-block-content container">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Business travel visualized</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              Layovers, cabin class, room accomodations&mdash;all of these are tangible experiences. Our system of visualizations let users
              actually see how their options play out.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block column column-block half-md hide-overflow purple">
          <div class="lazy-ratio full-height" data-width="146" data-height="150">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/upside/visualized-1.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-top">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/upside/visualized-2.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-bottom">
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="block dark-purple">
        <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="272" data-height="150">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/upside/section-6-1.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-delay sr-left">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/upside/section-6-2.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-delay sr-right">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/upside/section-6-3.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-bottom">
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="block padded">
        <div class="row container">
          <div class="inner-block column column-block align-self-center half-md two-third-xl">
            <div class="frame frame-desktop dark shadow sr-left lazy-ratio" data-width="1800" data-height="1016">
              <img class="inner-block-image" alt="Searching for flights loader screen" data-normal="./images/work/upside/find.jpg" data-srcset="
                  ./images/work/upside/find@0.5x.jpg 575w,
                  ./images/work/upside/find.jpg 1150w,
                  ./images/work/upside/find@1.5x.jpg 1725w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 90vw, (max-width: 1440px) 45vw, 810px">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md order-top-xs gutter-bottom-mobile column half-md one-third-xl">
            <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left">
              <h2 class="case-block-heading">Stop waiting, start finding</h2>
              <p class="case-block-text">
                A staggered approach to travel&mdash;airfare and hotel in separate steps&mdash;keeps the user engaged while cleverly doing
                work in the background. The result: a magically &lsquo;instant&rsquo; experience.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="case-referral row">
        <div class="inner-block padded column absolute-center-xs half-md purple">
          <div class="container">
            <p class="case-referral-blockquote">Brave was the best and brightest in the room.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block padded column half-md gray">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="case-referral-quote-icon"></div>
            <p class="case-referral-text">Brave does more than UX. They helped us think through the entire product — from design to user path to animation.
              When we needed a partner and some extra brainpower, Brave was the best and the brightest in the room.</p>
            <p class="case-referral-author">Scott Case,
              <em>President, Upside</em>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="cta-block padded">
        <a href="./work/homezen" class="cta-button cta-button-left" title="Previous Case">Previous Case</a>
        <div class="cta-content container">
          <div class="cta-text">Sometimes, you find something that just works.</div>
          <a href="/approach" class="btn btn-text icon-arrow">See Our Approach</a>
        </div>
        <a href="./work/felix" class="cta-button cta-button-right" title="Next Case">Next Case</a>
      </section>
      <%- include ../partials/_footer %>
    </main>

    <%- include ../partials/_footer-scripts %>

</body>

</html>